            On 8th June and 6th July 2023, the Regent team volunteered at MoNo Foods in Singapore. We provided valuable assistance by transporting, carrying, and sorting pallets of consumer goods at the MoNo Foods facility.
        </p>
        <p class="obiz">
            MoNo Foods&apos; mission is to change consumer mindsets regarding foods that have passed their best-before dates but are still safe for consumption by redistributing them to a community that supports food waste reduction.
