            This initiative not only addresses excessive food waste but also promotes sustainability and encourages mindful consumption.
        </p>
        <p class="obiz">
            The dedication of the Regent team serves as an inspiration for others to join the cause and work towards creating a more environmentally conscious and socially responsible society.
